            "weighted_score": 0.5081967115402222,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Total War: EMPIRE – Definitive Edition is rich with world history and pivotal events shat shaped the world we live in today. This game offers challenges for beginner's & advanced R.T.S. players with a passion for history and historical maneuvers. I have always enjoyed Real Time Strategy games, and this game holds many fond memories for my friends and me."
        },
