            "voted_up": false,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.4761904776096344,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "I cannot in good conscience recommend this game anymore. Back about 10 years ago the developers at CA went nuts and started changing their games to be PC instead of historically accurate. Before then I had bought every Total war game they made. When they went PC they started changing all their games to be Politically Correct they even changed the games that were already out. You didn't get a choice whether you wanted your games changed or not they just didn't care about their fans enough. And they have been going down hill ever since."
        },
